# st_snls  `v1.0.0`

jQuery st_snls script for create a empty container, Include custom style,custom option.
and callback when initial, Have fun!

See the [Demo Page](./preview.html).



## Quick start

1\.  Add latest jQuery and st_snls files

```html
<script src="../st_snls/module.js"></script>


<link href="../st_snls/css.css" rel="stylesheet">
```
![Quick start](data:image/png;base64,)


2\.  Create Elements

```html
<div class="fcl_lnls">
    <div class="fm-grp icon-inside">
        <label class="label inside req">1</label>
        <input type="text" class="fm-ctrl default" placeholder="/" value="2017/08/011" data-id='default'>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="fcl_lnls">
    <div class="fm-grp icon-inside">
        <label class="label inside req">2</label>
        <input type="text" class="fm-ctrl default1" placeholder="/" value="2017/08/011" data-id='default1'>
    </div>
</div>
```

    contentCss:'fz-md',

    callback: {

    }
})
